headline.main: US Factory Orders Up 1.2 Percent in January
headline.print_headline: US Factory Orders Up 1.2 Percent in January

lead_paragraph: U.S. businesses increased their orders in January, although a key component that tracks business investment spending fell for the first time in four months.
